    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted as a complete and structurally valid submission under ProfileMinimal. All 13 credibility factors have been addressed with documented status. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing acknowledged epistemic gaps at MRL 5 that preclude regulatory acceptance of the underlying model for its intended use, but the assessment process itself is accepted as fulfilling the submission requirements for this review stage. Package integrity is confirmed via SHA-256 hash.",
